name: Qbiki
overview:
SeattleClouds provides an online iPhone application designer. SeattleClouds is the first online tool that allows designing, building and previewing of iPhone apps for a very low price. SeattleClouds online designer is an WYSIWYG html editor, very easy to use that allows everyone to edit iPhone application content, preview it in a web simulator and immediately preview it on iPhone, using our SeattleClouds iPhone app.

This designer is an invaluable tool for small businesses, organizations and institutions, bands, musicians, book publishers, etc who are willing to publish their content as an iPhone app. The service is inexpensive and can be handled by anyone.

Our company is founded by 3 iPhone developers. We also provide services of building custom iPhone applications on a contract basis.
